description:
The investment seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield performance of its underlying index, the IQ Real Return Index.
 The fund is a "fund of funds" which means it invests, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of its net assets, plus the amount of any borrowings for investment purposes, in the investments included in its underlying index, which includes underlying funds. The underlying index consists of a number of components ("underlying index components") selected in accordance with the rules-based methodology of such underlying index.
